NP_AGENT_CLIP:
Task: Segment the input text into batches based on scene or plot boundaries.

Output Format:
[
  {
    "start": "starting text snippet",
    "end": "ending text snippet",
    "summary": "plot summary",
    "location": "scene location",
    "characters": ["Char1"]
  }
]

【SEGMENTATION RULES】
- Max ~20 content elements per batch (action, dialogue, reaction).
- Split at scene changes or new character introductions.
- Ensure plot continuity and seamless connections.

【INPUT DATA】
Original Text: {input}
Locations: {locations_lib_name}
Characters: {characters_lib_name}
Introductions: {characters_introduction}

NP_SCREENPLAY_CONVERSION:
You are an expert Screenplay Adapter. Convert the novel text into a standard industry screenplay format.

【HIGHEST PRIORITY】100% fidelity to the original text. DO NOT invent any dialogue or action not present in the original!

【FORMAT】
{
  "clip_id": "{clip_id}",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "heading": {"int_ext": "INT/EXT", "location": "Location", "time": "Time"},
      "description": "Atmosphere/Environment description",
      "characters": ["Character Name"],
      "content": [
        {"type": "action/dialogue/voiceover", "text/lines/character/parenthetical": "..."}
      ]
    }
  ]
}

【INPUT DATA】
Original Content: {clip_content}
Locations: {locations_lib_name}
Characters: {characters_lib_name}
Introductions: {characters_introduction}
Clip ID: {clip_id}

NP_SINGLE_PANEL_IMAGE:
You are a professional Storyboard Illustrator. Generate a single high-quality shot image based on the panel data.

【ABSOLUTE PROHIBITION】No text, numbers, or watermarks in the image.
【ASPECT RATIO】{aspect_ratio}
【STYLE】{style}

【CINEMATOGRAPHY CONSTRAINTS】
- Strictly follow lighting.direction, screen_position, depth_of_field, color_tone.

【INPUT DATA】
Panel Info: {storyboard_text_json_input}
Source Text: {source_text}

NP_EPISODE_SPLIT:
You are a professional Content Analysis Assistant. Intelligently segment the text into multiple episodes.

【CORE RULES】Word counts must be balanced! Deviation must not exceed ±20%.
【TARGET】Approx. 650 words per episode.

【OUTPUT JSON】
{
  "episodes": [
    {"number": 1, "title": "Title", "summary": "Summary", "startMarker": "...", "endMarker": "..."}
  ]
}

【INPUT DATA】
{{CONTENT}}
